WEBVTT

01:36.400 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:38.360 --> 01:39.320
During the winter holiday,

01:40.320 --> 01:42.160
first, stay safe.

01:42.240 --> 01:43.960
Also, keep your emotions in check.

01:44.040 --> 01:45.800
Don't just focus on having fun.

01:46.520 --> 01:48.040
You're in your first year
of high school now.

01:48.120 --> 01:50.200
But before you know it,
you'll be in the second year.

01:50.280 --> 01:51.400
What's going to happen next?

01:51.480 --> 01:52.800
Then, the third year will be here.

01:52.880 --> 01:55.320
Are you going to spend three whole years

01:55.400 --> 01:56.800
fighting for the college entrance exam

01:56.880 --> 01:58.360
or just put in the last year's effort?

01:58.440 --> 01:59.840
You can calculate it yourself.

02:04.080 --> 02:05.840
The effort you put into your studies

02:05.920 --> 02:09.039
will show in the results on exam day.

02:09.720 --> 02:11.240
I was pretty impressive
when I was your age.

02:11.320 --> 02:13.600
I started putting in the effort
back in my first year.

02:13.680 --> 02:15.960
If you listen, it's on you.
If not, it's on me.

02:16.040 --> 02:16.960
Class is over!

02:19.920 --> 02:22.840
Why do you have so few textbooks?

02:24.640 --> 02:26.200
I took most of them home a few days ago.

02:27.600 --> 02:28.760
Even just a few days ago,
they were that few.

02:29.440 --> 02:31.040
I started collecting them a few days ago.

02:31.720 --> 02:33.280
I like to study like crazy at home.

02:34.800 --> 02:35.760
You care so much about me?

02:38.400 --> 02:39.880
Sang Yan, let's go play basketball!

02:40.880 --> 02:42.920
Let's crush the guys
from No. 2 High School!

02:44.560 --> 02:47.640
I'm not going. I'm heading home
and hitting the books.

02:52.920 --> 02:54.640
Bro, did you catch some terminal illness?

02:55.240 --> 02:57.080
Or are you suddenly having
a burst of energy to study?

02:57.160 --> 02:59.920
Whatever happens, I'll give you a big hug.

03:02.200 --> 03:03.440
Are you insane?

03:03.520 --> 03:04.360
Get lost.

03:05.280 --> 03:06.560
Where to? To the court?

03:06.640 --> 03:07.640
I'm leaving!

03:07.720 --> 03:08.720
Sang Yan!

03:08.800 --> 03:10.080
Sang Yan!

03:27.920 --> 03:31.040
You're not studying properly anymore,

03:31.640 --> 03:33.080
not even playing basketball,

03:33.960 --> 03:35.360
just learning how to stalk people, huh?

03:36.120 --> 03:37.480
I am…

03:37.560 --> 03:39.080
I am going to take the bus.

03:39.160 --> 03:40.680
I live in the same direction.

03:41.360 --> 03:43.840
How come I've never seen you on the bus?

03:45.560 --> 03:47.800
So, you've been searching for me?

03:49.000 --> 03:51.120
I just mean I don't remember.

03:51.640 --> 03:53.440
Next time, look carefully.

03:53.520 --> 03:55.000
Why should I look carefully?

03:55.600 --> 03:57.480
So you won't miss out

03:57.560 --> 03:59.720
the chance to go to school with me.

04:02.720 --> 04:04.800
- Where do you live?
- What for?

04:05.480 --> 04:07.480
Next time when I reach your stop,

04:07.560 --> 04:08.920
I'll pay more attention.

04:26.640 --> 04:27.920
3,068 DAYS

04:42.480 --> 04:44.000
Sorry. I didn't know
what you all liked to eat.

04:44.080 --> 04:45.240
So, I didn't get anything for you.

04:45.320 --> 04:47.760
I remember
you don't like cilantro and garlic.

04:48.280 --> 04:49.720
Thanks.

04:53.040 --> 04:55.000
I don't like them either.

04:55.960 --> 04:57.520
Sorry, I forgot.
Let me pick it out for you.

04:58.880 --> 04:59.800
Xiang Lang,

04:59.880 --> 05:02.280
you're like you're taking care
of two wives.

05:04.720 --> 05:05.960
Dian, Qiao, and I

05:06.040 --> 05:07.920
have been looking after each other
since kindergarten.

05:08.000 --> 05:08.880
We've been used to it.

05:08.960 --> 05:11.840
I often hear you guys
call Wen Yifan "Dian."

05:11.920 --> 05:13.320
Is it her nickname from kindergarten?

05:14.480 --> 05:15.880
Actually, it's a funny story.

05:15.960 --> 05:17.040
Back in kindergarten,

05:17.120 --> 05:19.120
she used to write "Yi"
in her name as four dots (Dians).

05:19.200 --> 05:22.200
Put them together and it becomes
Wen "Dian Dian Dian Dian" Fan.

05:22.800 --> 05:23.760
Wait, no.

05:23.840 --> 05:26.280
It should be called
Wen "Dian Dian Dian Dian Dian."

05:26.360 --> 05:27.840
"Fan" also has one dot.

05:29.520 --> 05:30.680
Thanks.

05:33.200 --> 05:34.240
Done or not?

05:34.920 --> 05:35.920
It's fine.

05:36.520 --> 05:37.440
Look at them.

05:38.400 --> 05:40.320
Look at their family of three.

05:40.400 --> 05:41.560
Dian, here.

05:42.480 --> 05:44.200
Now look at us two.

05:45.960 --> 05:48.400
Fine. Then I'll leave home.

05:54.720 --> 05:55.640
Eat up.

05:55.720 --> 05:57.520
Eating will shut you up.

05:57.600 --> 05:58.800
After eating, we'll go to Overtime.

05:58.880 --> 06:00.080
I reserved a private room for you.

06:20.040 --> 06:21.080
It's a rotating turntable.

06:24.280 --> 06:26.840
OVERTIME

06:27.880 --> 06:30.560
Dian, do you think living
with Sang Yan would be miserable?

06:30.640 --> 06:32.400
Why do you ask that?

06:32.480 --> 06:34.920
He didn't even smile
while eating just now.

06:35.000 --> 06:36.560
He looked like someone owed him a fortune.

06:37.240 --> 06:38.080
Really?

06:39.000 --> 06:41.560
I feel like he's pretty proud.

06:42.600 --> 06:44.320
Isn't he always like this?

06:45.320 --> 06:47.640
How about you live
at Xiang Lang's place instead?

06:49.680 --> 06:52.320
What I mean is,
you swap places with Xiang Lang.

06:52.400 --> 06:53.480
Let Xiang Lang live with Sang Yan.

06:55.760 --> 06:56.840
I can do that.

06:58.200 --> 06:59.760
Forget it. Too much trouble.

07:02.480 --> 07:03.760
They're here.

07:03.840 --> 07:05.080
Let's stop talking about this.

07:07.040 --> 07:07.960
Come on, everyone.

07:08.040 --> 07:10.080
Try our new products.

07:10.160 --> 07:11.000
Yu Zhuo, introduce them.

07:11.080 --> 07:12.800
This cup is for me.

07:12.880 --> 07:14.000
It's called "Allergic to Work."

07:14.080 --> 07:16.040
This cup is called "Paid to Slack off."

07:16.120 --> 07:17.000
Thanks.

07:17.080 --> 07:19.800
This cup is called "Why Overcompetition?"

07:20.560 --> 07:23.240
This cup is called
"Reject False Promises."

07:24.360 --> 07:26.120
- This cup is called…
- Wait a minute.

07:26.720 --> 07:28.680
Who came up with these names?

07:28.760 --> 07:29.920
I did. How's that?

07:30.920 --> 07:32.800
- This cup is called…
- "Better off Skipping Work."

07:34.560 --> 07:36.200
Let's play Truth or Dare.

07:36.280 --> 07:37.320
What do you think?

07:37.400 --> 07:39.120
Sure. But do you know how to play?

07:39.200 --> 07:40.760
Who do you think
you're looking down on? Come on.

07:41.560 --> 07:43.880
- I don't know how to play.
- No worries. We've got your back.

07:45.120 --> 07:46.760
Xiang Lang,
you're the guest. You go first.

07:46.840 --> 07:47.760
Here.

07:51.200 --> 07:53.280
- Five sixs.
- Eight sixs.

07:53.360 --> 07:54.200
Ten.

08:02.720 --> 08:03.760
Start.

08:05.400 --> 08:06.720
Start?

08:06.800 --> 08:08.840
This is just the first round
and you're already calling me out?

08:11.560 --> 08:12.560
Let's wait and see.

08:12.640 --> 08:13.720
Here.

08:15.280 --> 08:18.080
Nine sixs. Su Haoan,
you're off to a bad start.

08:18.160 --> 08:19.080
Truth or Dare?

08:19.160 --> 08:20.320
This is a weird one.

08:20.400 --> 08:21.240
Dare.

08:24.240 --> 08:25.440
Take a look.

08:26.040 --> 08:27.840
Choose someone here…

08:29.920 --> 08:30.960
and kiss them.

08:31.720 --> 08:34.039
You're not chickening out, are you?

08:34.120 --> 08:35.760
Who said I can't play?

08:44.560 --> 08:47.680
I'll go all in. Bro, help me out!

08:48.360 --> 08:49.280
Who else would I kiss if not you?

08:49.360 --> 08:51.760
You've kissed Duan Jiaxu while
playing games in college, haven't you?

08:51.840 --> 08:53.840
Really? You and Duan Jiaxu?

08:53.920 --> 08:55.480
You know him, too?

08:55.560 --> 08:57.320
You forgot I'm also from Nanwu University.

08:57.400 --> 08:59.400
They're in the same department,
same class,

08:59.480 --> 09:00.880
even the same dorm.

09:00.960 --> 09:02.480
They're both Computer Science majors.

09:09.680 --> 09:11.880
Well done! See? I'm brave enough to play.

09:14.000 --> 09:15.200
Let's go. Next round.

09:18.320 --> 09:19.400
Here.

09:21.160 --> 09:23.120
Let's go… Next round.

09:34.000 --> 09:35.600
- Six twos.
- Six threes.

09:35.680 --> 09:37.080
- Seven threes.
- Start.

09:39.400 --> 09:40.440
Start?

09:41.200 --> 09:42.720
You're calling it so soon, Wen Yifan?

09:45.040 --> 09:47.440
Truth or Dare?

09:48.440 --> 09:49.520
Truth.

09:49.600 --> 09:50.520
Then let me pick for you.

09:51.400 --> 09:54.360
Tell us one good trait

09:54.440 --> 09:55.600
about every man here.

09:58.040 --> 09:59.000
Let's start with Su Haoan.

10:02.120 --> 10:02.960
Rich.

10:05.000 --> 10:05.880
What about Xiang Lang?

10:08.080 --> 10:11.120
Smart, handsome, and considerate.

10:11.200 --> 10:12.200
I thought you were only
supposed to say one?

10:14.360 --> 10:15.680
What about Sang Yan?

10:19.920 --> 10:20.760
Calm…

10:21.480 --> 10:23.440
Quiet… Confident…

10:27.920 --> 10:29.560
- Just confident.
- Too confident.

10:36.880 --> 10:37.720
Twelve sixs.

10:40.680 --> 10:41.520
Dian,

10:42.720 --> 10:44.240
- don't be too eager…
- Fifteen sixs.

10:44.840 --> 10:46.520
You really dare to call it?

10:47.120 --> 10:48.560
I dare. Do you dare to open it?

10:48.640 --> 10:49.800
What's there to be afraid of?

10:49.880 --> 10:50.840
Open it.

10:59.200 --> 11:01.480
Five sixs. You won!

11:03.440 --> 11:06.480
Xiang Lang, I told you!
You fell for his trick.

11:06.560 --> 11:07.440
Truth or Dare?

11:08.840 --> 11:10.000
Truth.

11:10.680 --> 11:13.560
Tell us one thing you regret the most.

11:14.600 --> 11:15.960
The biggest regret?

11:16.720 --> 11:18.400
It's probably studying abroad.

11:18.480 --> 11:20.320
I was supposed to go to Yihe University

11:20.400 --> 11:21.840
with Dian.

11:25.440 --> 11:26.280
Why did you choose Yihe University?

11:28.960 --> 11:30.440
I had already made plans
with someone else.

11:30.520 --> 11:33.040
Dian was supposed to go
to Nanwu University with me.

11:33.120 --> 11:35.000
Who knew she suddenly
went to Yihe University.

11:35.720 --> 11:37.040
I had already applied

11:37.120 --> 11:39.320
for the best program
at Yihe, Clinical Medicine,

11:39.400 --> 11:42.040
but my parents insisted I go abroad.

11:42.120 --> 11:44.520
Otherwise,
from kindergarten to university,

11:44.600 --> 11:45.960
we would have been classmates
the whole time.

11:46.040 --> 11:47.040
Real childhood sweethearts.

11:56.400 --> 11:57.440
Let's continue.

11:58.240 --> 11:59.360
Yes, let's continue.

11:59.440 --> 12:01.120
Let's make this round more exciting.

12:01.200 --> 12:02.440
We'll double the penalty for the loser,

12:02.520 --> 12:03.640
both Truth and Dare. What do you think?

12:06.960 --> 12:07.800
Six threes.

12:07.880 --> 12:09.280
Ten fours.

12:10.040 --> 12:11.080
Ten fives!

12:16.320 --> 12:19.640
Fifteen…

12:19.720 --> 12:20.760
Twenty sixs.

12:31.040 --> 12:32.200
Start.

12:35.040 --> 12:37.160
- I lost.
- Yeah, you finally lost.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.080
No regrets in my life.

12:38.160 --> 12:40.040
Come on, Truth and Dare.

12:40.640 --> 12:41.600
Let's do truth first.

12:44.800 --> 12:47.480
The last city you flew to?

12:47.560 --> 12:48.920
What a boring question. Who cares?

12:50.560 --> 12:51.400
Yihe.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.960
You paid for the bill, right?

13:26.040 --> 13:27.440
Let's split it three ways.

13:27.520 --> 13:29.000
The front desk said Sang Yan already paid.

13:30.400 --> 13:31.480
He did?

13:32.160 --> 13:33.920
I thought Sang Yan
only gave a 90% discount

13:34.000 --> 13:34.840
and he was so stingy.

13:34.920 --> 13:36.360
Looks like I wrongly accused him.

13:36.880 --> 13:39.080
How about we leave
a five-star review for him?

13:39.160 --> 13:40.680
We can't take advantage of him for free.

13:41.440 --> 13:42.480
I'll take a call.

13:43.200 --> 13:44.280
Hello, Ms. Qian?

13:45.680 --> 13:46.600
Okay, I got it.

13:46.680 --> 13:48.480
I'll take care of it right away.

13:50.800 --> 13:53.040
I got an urgent task.
I need to go home and finish an article.

13:53.960 --> 13:55.200
Let me give you a ride.
You'll get home faster.

13:55.280 --> 13:56.480
Sure.

13:56.560 --> 13:58.240
Take care.

13:58.320 --> 13:59.440
I'll take a few pictures for him.

13:59.520 --> 14:01.000
Okay. Bye.

14:01.560 --> 14:02.400
Bye.

14:03.560 --> 14:04.880
Be careful on your way.

14:04.960 --> 14:06.640
Okay. You take care, too.

14:09.120 --> 14:10.160
Let's go.

14:27.280 --> 14:28.320
Zhong Siqiao!

14:28.920 --> 14:29.880
Why are you still here?

14:31.320 --> 14:32.600
You already treated us.

14:32.680 --> 14:34.800
Shouldn't I take some photos for you
and recommend it?

14:34.880 --> 14:36.240
It's great.

14:37.040 --> 14:37.880
Let me buy you another drink.

14:39.920 --> 14:40.840
Wait a minute.

14:40.920 --> 14:42.000
What's up?

14:42.800 --> 14:46.040
Didn't we agree
we wouldn't drink together again?

14:47.360 --> 14:48.480
Oh.

14:48.560 --> 14:49.400
Right.

14:52.040 --> 14:54.000
You drink then. You're the guest.

14:55.320 --> 14:57.080
Or you drink. You just had a breakup.

14:57.160 --> 14:58.080
Let the alcohol cure your sorrow.

14:59.320 --> 15:01.000
One drink's enough.

15:01.080 --> 15:02.640
I can't keep using alcohol
to drown my sorrows.

15:07.400 --> 15:08.440
Let me ask you.

15:09.040 --> 15:10.760
Don't you feel like
everyone's acting a little strange today?

15:12.720 --> 15:14.080
Yeah, a little.

15:17.760 --> 15:19.160
Let me ask you again.

15:19.240 --> 15:20.960
Why didn't Wen Yifan
go to Nanwu University?

15:21.600 --> 15:23.280
Her grades are so much higher.

15:24.760 --> 15:26.720
I'm her good friend,

15:26.800 --> 15:28.320
but I don't get it either.

15:28.400 --> 15:29.840
I feel like she just wants

15:29.920 --> 15:31.400
to keep her distance from everyone.

15:31.480 --> 15:33.120
Even I haven't heard from her much.

15:34.280 --> 15:35.240
I thought

15:35.320 --> 15:37.480
when people grow up,
their feelings change.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.880
I really hate this change.

15:42.320 --> 15:43.400
Do you believe me?

15:43.920 --> 15:45.400
Every time I date,

15:45.480 --> 15:47.320
I hope the current one is the last.

15:48.280 --> 15:49.440
But nowadays,

15:49.520 --> 15:51.760
no one believes
that love should be timeless.

15:51.840 --> 15:53.160
If you keep acting like this,

15:53.240 --> 15:54.680
it'll put a lot of pressure
on your partner.

15:55.880 --> 15:57.720
What's wrong with wanting
to spend a lifetime together?

16:01.520 --> 16:03.320
Maybe you just haven't met
the right person yet.

16:03.400 --> 16:05.040
It's you who hasn't met the right person.

16:05.120 --> 16:06.720
Why are you pulling me into this?

16:06.800 --> 16:09.000
I'd rather not date
than settle for the wrong person.

16:22.520 --> 16:23.800
You're still not going home?

16:27.120 --> 16:28.040
What about them?

16:28.680 --> 16:29.520
They've gone back.

16:31.440 --> 16:32.440
I want to ask you something.

16:33.400 --> 16:34.760
You still like Wen Yifan, right?

16:38.600 --> 16:40.560
I just feel like
you still have feelings for her.

16:40.640 --> 16:42.720
That's why I tried
to set you up to be roommates.

16:45.440 --> 16:46.840
I've said this so many times.

16:48.080 --> 16:50.320
We're roommates, just roommates.

16:51.440 --> 16:52.480
Enough.

16:53.920 --> 16:56.120
I can tell you're not okay.

16:59.600 --> 17:01.880
For example? What's not okay?

17:03.320 --> 17:04.319
The way you looked at Xiang Lang.

17:04.400 --> 17:06.319
You didn't like anything about him.

17:06.400 --> 17:07.880
Weren't you jealous of him?

17:12.000 --> 17:13.760
Are you insane?

17:15.880 --> 17:17.119
Keep being stubborn.

17:17.920 --> 17:20.000
I've seen you in this
awful state before, after all.

17:21.000 --> 17:21.880
The last time

17:21.960 --> 17:23.720
was the day the college
entrance results came out.

17:23.800 --> 17:24.720
Do you still remember?

17:32.560 --> 17:38.800
BEIYU

17:44.240 --> 17:46.160
You've been
quite busy lately, haven't you?

17:46.240 --> 17:48.160
I've been unable to reach you.

17:49.000 --> 17:49.840
What happened to you?

17:51.880 --> 17:52.880
Nothing.

17:53.800 --> 17:54.640
My phone broke.

18:03.960 --> 18:05.040
Why are you here?

18:15.200 --> 18:17.520
Earlier, didn't we agree on this?

18:18.120 --> 18:20.520
After the admission results come out,
I'd come to visit.

18:21.680 --> 18:22.560
My results are in.

18:23.520 --> 18:25.680
I got into Nanwu University,
Computer Science department.

18:26.320 --> 18:27.680
Your grades are better than mine.

18:27.760 --> 18:28.680
You'll easily get into
the program you want…

18:28.760 --> 18:29.600
Sang Yan,

18:32.840 --> 18:34.400
I didn't apply to Nanwu University.

18:37.440 --> 18:39.440
- You're kidding, right?
- No.

18:42.400 --> 18:43.360
Then, where did you apply?

18:45.760 --> 18:46.800
Yihe University.

18:49.720 --> 18:50.560
Why?

18:52.320 --> 18:53.560
Why Yihe University?

18:58.440 --> 18:59.800
I had already made plans
with someone else.

19:01.840 --> 19:04.440
You came back so late.
Our parents will be concerned.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.640
Do you want some jelly?

19:07.680 --> 19:09.560
Haoan is already waiting for you.

19:09.640 --> 19:11.560
Does Haoan want some jelly, too?

19:27.600 --> 19:28.600
What about me?

19:29.880 --> 19:31.400
Don't you want to say anything to me?

19:33.000 --> 19:34.520
Well, I'll say it straight.

19:35.720 --> 19:36.640
Sang Yan.

19:38.240 --> 19:39.600
I really hate it,

19:40.720 --> 19:42.280
and I really dislike it

19:42.880 --> 19:44.400
that you always
come looking for me in Beiyu.

19:48.040 --> 19:49.360
It's annoying

19:50.040 --> 19:51.880
to come out to meet you every time.

19:54.720 --> 19:55.640
Wen Yifan,

19:59.960 --> 20:01.400
am I just your backup option?

20:04.520 --> 20:06.040
Nanwu is closer to Beiyu.

20:06.120 --> 20:07.960
So, I'll go somewhere farther away.

20:08.640 --> 20:10.240
When I get to Yihe,

20:10.920 --> 20:13.360
I hope you won't come looking for me
like this anymore.

20:17.560 --> 20:18.520
You're back.

20:20.640 --> 20:21.760
You didn't reply on WeChat

20:21.840 --> 20:23.800
and didn't answer my calls.

20:24.520 --> 20:26.360
Where have you been?

20:26.440 --> 20:27.600
What are you doing here?

20:35.440 --> 20:37.120
I got into Nanwu University.

20:38.360 --> 20:40.960
Nanwu University!

20:46.200 --> 20:47.040
What's your attitude about this?

20:53.200 --> 20:54.240
Bro, think about it.

20:54.320 --> 20:55.720
We can still be classmates!

20:55.800 --> 20:57.400
You know how bad my grades were.

20:57.480 --> 20:58.520
Getting into Nanwu University

20:58.600 --> 21:00.600
will make my grandparents so happy!

21:01.120 --> 21:03.520
You know what? When you said
you were going to Nanwu University,

21:03.600 --> 21:04.920
I thought, how good is Nanwu University?

21:05.000 --> 21:05.840
Still playing games?

21:37.720 --> 21:38.760
Dian.

21:43.000 --> 21:43.920
Nothing.

21:52.960 --> 21:54.480
You're still the same as before.

21:56.360 --> 21:59.000
It seems nothing matters to you,

22:00.480 --> 22:01.840
and you're not interested

22:01.920 --> 22:02.880
in anything.

22:03.760 --> 22:04.800
I'm actually quite curious.

22:05.560 --> 22:06.680
What exactly would it take

22:07.360 --> 22:08.320
to get your attention?

22:08.400 --> 22:10.320
It's not as exaggerated as you say.

22:13.800 --> 22:15.000
Then tell me.

22:16.040 --> 22:18.880
How's it been since you returned to Nanwu?

22:18.960 --> 22:20.040
Pretty good.

22:22.880 --> 22:23.960
Always "pretty good."

22:24.840 --> 22:26.280
Every time I ask,
it's always "pretty good."

22:26.920 --> 22:28.360
When I was abroad,
you were just as half-hearted.

22:29.040 --> 22:31.800
In our group of three,
only Qiao and I were talking.

22:32.640 --> 22:34.400
You always just replied something

22:34.480 --> 22:36.720
like "okay," "yeah," "nice."

22:37.240 --> 22:38.600
You never talk about your own stuff.

22:40.760 --> 22:42.320
My life is pretty boring.

22:42.400 --> 22:43.800
Even boring things can be talked about.

22:47.600 --> 22:48.880
Our world is like this.

22:48.960 --> 22:51.760
If we're happy, we laugh.
If we're sad, we cry.

22:54.120 --> 22:56.160
You seem like someone
from a completely different world.

23:05.680 --> 23:06.560
Dian,

23:07.920 --> 23:09.280
can you promise me one thing?

23:11.520 --> 23:12.680
What is it?

23:14.240 --> 23:15.680
In the future,

23:15.760 --> 23:18.280
if you encounter any difficulties,

23:18.840 --> 23:19.720
tell me right away.

23:22.840 --> 23:25.120
I don't want you to always shut me out.

23:28.120 --> 23:28.960
Okay.

23:30.560 --> 23:31.760
Can you explain one thing?

23:31.840 --> 23:36.040
You always wanted to go
to Nanwu University.

23:36.120 --> 23:39.800
Why did you end up
quietly switching to Yihe University?

23:41.640 --> 23:42.960
Don't you feel regretful?

23:47.600 --> 23:49.160
You know it's a regret,

23:49.240 --> 23:50.400
then why bring it up again?

23:56.200 --> 23:58.840
Hey, when are you two
going to Nanwu University?

23:58.920 --> 24:00.680
Didn't I tell you? We're leaving tomorrow.

24:00.760 --> 24:03.400
We did it!

24:03.480 --> 24:05.160
- Shout it louder!
- We did it!

24:05.240 --> 24:06.120
We did it!

24:13.680 --> 24:15.360
One, two, three!

24:18.320 --> 24:20.360
I will definitely
get into Nanwu University.

24:20.440 --> 24:22.000
And I believe you will, too.

24:24.880 --> 24:26.680
So, let's make a promise

24:26.760 --> 24:29.280
to work hard together
and get into Nanwu University.

24:32.520 --> 24:34.520
I will definitely
get into Nanwu University.

24:36.520 --> 24:38.720
- I'll take your basketball.
- Why?

24:38.800 --> 24:40.920
Why? Focus on studying!

24:41.000 --> 24:42.200
Don't you want to get
into Nanwu University?

25:13.560 --> 25:15.480
Didn't we agree to report?

25:33.560 --> 25:35.760
I WON'T COME BACK TONIGHT
JUST LOCK THE DOOR

25:44.240 --> 25:46.760
YOU REALLY KEEP YOUR PROMISES

25:58.480 --> 26:00.960
OKAY

26:04.760 --> 26:06.040
I WON'T COME BACK TONIGHT
JUST LOCK THE DOOR

26:06.120 --> 26:07.400
OKAY

26:39.320 --> 26:40.280
I WON'T COME BACK TONIGHT
JUST LOCK THE DOOR

26:40.360 --> 26:41.200
OKAY

26:51.280 --> 26:54.000
Zhang, we have eight topics
to choose from this time.

26:54.080 --> 26:55.760
I'll do the first four with Yifan.

26:55.840 --> 26:57.560
You two can do the rest.

27:38.400 --> 27:40.080
SANG YAN:
NOT COMING BACK TONIGHT, LOCK THE DOOR

27:40.160 --> 27:41.800
WEN YIFAN: OKAY

27:41.880 --> 27:46.680
TO THE BATTLEFIELD

27:54.280 --> 27:56.600
The potatoes here are really delicious.
Want to try a piece?

28:00.800 --> 28:02.000
Your roommate finally replied
to your WeChat?

28:06.480 --> 28:07.760
NOT COMING BACK TONIGHT
LOCK THE DOOR

28:07.840 --> 28:09.080
OKAY

28:22.680 --> 28:24.840
Yan, you're so early today.

28:24.920 --> 28:26.520
Isn't school just starting?

28:27.960 --> 28:30.040
It's the second year of high school.
If I go early, I can learn a bit more.

28:30.120 --> 28:31.400
But I haven't even made breakfast yet.

28:31.480 --> 28:33.360
I'll buy something on the way.

28:33.440 --> 28:34.680
- I'm off.
- Take it easy.

29:10.240 --> 29:11.880
Handsome, can I sit here?

29:16.040 --> 29:17.760
Miss. Miss.

29:22.440 --> 29:23.520
Thank you.

29:52.320 --> 29:53.280
Wen Yifan.

29:54.080 --> 29:55.000
There's a place there.

30:12.520 --> 30:13.680
Why don't you sit?

30:16.120 --> 30:17.800
If I sit for too long,
my legs will fall asleep.

31:23.760 --> 31:25.000
NOT COMING BACK TONIGHT. LOCK THE DOOR
OKAY

31:25.080 --> 31:27.280
SANG YAN: NOT COMING BACK
LOCK THE DOOR

31:27.360 --> 31:30.320
WEN YIFAN: OKAY

31:35.360 --> 31:36.960
Miss Wen, someone's looking for you.

31:37.040 --> 31:38.320
She's waiting over there.

31:39.640 --> 31:40.520
Jiang,

31:41.360 --> 31:43.600
I thought you were still at Yihe.

31:43.680 --> 31:44.800
How long have you been here?

31:45.360 --> 31:46.960
Return the equipment first.

31:47.040 --> 31:48.400
- Okay.
- Thank you.

31:50.120 --> 31:51.360
Stay safe on your way!

31:56.080 --> 31:57.920
I heard from Jia

31:58.520 --> 32:00.320
that she saw you at the city hospital.

32:00.840 --> 32:02.080
I saw your equipment bag

32:02.160 --> 32:03.160
with the TV station logo on it.

32:03.840 --> 32:06.400
So, I came over to try my luck.

32:07.520 --> 32:08.880
What do you need me for?

32:10.240 --> 32:12.480
It's Little New Year today, right?

32:12.560 --> 32:13.840
And Spring Festival is almost here.

32:15.880 --> 32:18.040
How about spending
New Year's Eve at my place?

32:18.600 --> 32:21.080
Also, I want to introduce someone to you.

32:21.160 --> 32:23.000
I'm fine on my own.
You don't need to worry about me.

32:23.080 --> 32:24.760
That's not what I meant.

32:24.840 --> 32:25.920
You'll understand when you get here.

32:27.280 --> 32:29.680
Jia also asked me to invite you.

32:35.000 --> 32:37.280
Looks like you got approval
from Zheng Kejia.

32:40.960 --> 32:43.280
Um… I was worried about

32:43.880 --> 32:45.840
your bad mood.
I didn't want it to affect your emotions.

32:45.920 --> 32:47.880
That's why I first asked Jia.

32:50.560 --> 32:52.600
- I'll go to work now.
- Jiang!

32:53.920 --> 32:54.760
Are you…

32:55.320 --> 32:57.520
Are you still mad at me?

32:58.560 --> 33:00.000
I know that all these years,

33:00.080 --> 33:01.960
I've owed you too much.

33:04.560 --> 33:07.480
How… How can I make it up to you?

33:09.040 --> 33:10.320
I've already forgiven you.

33:11.040 --> 33:13.200
You had the right
to choose your happiness.

33:13.280 --> 33:14.120
I'm fine now.

33:17.240 --> 33:18.160
So,

33:18.960 --> 33:21.560
does that mean
you'll come home for New Year's Eve?

33:23.880 --> 33:24.760
I'll think about it.

33:25.680 --> 33:27.360
Please go back. It's so cold out.

33:27.960 --> 33:29.760
- Oh… Hey…
- Stay safe on your way!

33:29.840 --> 33:30.920
When the time comes,

33:32.040 --> 33:34.560
tell me what you want to eat, Jiang.

33:34.640 --> 33:37.240
Let me know when you're off
for Spring Festival break!

33:49.200 --> 33:50.280
Who is he?

33:50.360 --> 33:51.720
Sang Yan. Can't you recognize him?

33:52.360 --> 33:54.040
He's been sleeping for several days.

33:54.120 --> 33:55.080
If he keeps this up,

33:55.160 --> 33:56.400
he'll probably spend
the Spring Festival here.

34:16.960 --> 34:18.400
Dian, I need to ask you.

34:18.480 --> 34:21.080
Did you have an argument with Sang Yan?

34:21.159 --> 34:22.040
No.

34:22.560 --> 34:23.400
Then why has he been

34:23.480 --> 34:24.400
sleeping at Overtime, not going back home?

34:24.480 --> 34:26.040
He's been sleeping at Overtime?

34:26.120 --> 34:27.080
Yes.

34:27.679 --> 34:29.080
If Sang Yan bullies you,

34:29.159 --> 34:31.120
you must let me know.
I won't let him off the hook.

34:31.199 --> 34:32.040
You're overthinking.

34:33.040 --> 34:34.320
- Come here.
- It's not that I think too much.

34:34.400 --> 34:36.600
- What's wrong?
- It's just that you never tell me anything

34:36.679 --> 34:38.440
about how you two get along.

34:38.520 --> 34:40.159
We're not really getting along.

34:41.239 --> 34:42.920
Actually, I think

34:43.000 --> 34:45.199
we're more like

34:46.400 --> 34:48.360
two strangers under one roof.

34:49.760 --> 34:51.600
And we don't really talk much.

34:52.560 --> 34:54.840
Dian, let's leave it at that. Bye then.

35:02.360 --> 35:04.840
LOCK THE DOOR

35:06.440 --> 35:07.600
Not coming back again?

35:12.560 --> 35:15.880
OKAY

35:28.760 --> 35:30.760
Thanks for helping
with the Overtime photoshoot.

35:31.360 --> 35:32.200
No problem.

35:32.280 --> 35:33.800
You can go back now.
No need to walk me out.

35:34.720 --> 35:37.760
Do you always walk every girl home?

35:38.680 --> 35:39.560
You're a girl.

35:39.640 --> 35:41.960
It's not safe to walk home alone at night.

35:43.400 --> 35:44.720
You're a guy.

35:44.800 --> 35:46.800
Be mindful of what you say.

35:46.880 --> 35:48.440
Don't act all macho.

35:52.920 --> 35:54.080
You don't need to walk me out.

35:54.160 --> 35:56.360
- My house is just up ahead.
- Qiao,

35:56.960 --> 35:58.360
where are you going?

35:58.440 --> 35:59.400
Why aren't you coming home?

36:00.760 --> 36:02.120
Is that your friend?

36:03.040 --> 36:04.640
Yeah, friend!

36:06.120 --> 36:07.080
Hello!

36:08.000 --> 36:09.800
Auntie, who's that?

36:09.880 --> 36:11.320
Is that your boyfriend?

36:12.280 --> 36:14.320
Stop making things up!

36:14.400 --> 36:16.320
So, your house is around here?

36:17.400 --> 36:18.760
Come in for tea!

36:19.280 --> 36:21.640
- Don't be shy. Come in!
- Okay!

36:21.720 --> 36:23.000
Stop looking.

36:23.560 --> 36:25.480
You don't really want tea, do you?

36:25.560 --> 36:27.200
Of course, I don't.

36:27.280 --> 36:28.480
I just don't want them to overthink it.

36:28.560 --> 36:30.080
That'll definitely make them think.

36:31.120 --> 36:32.280
Well, I'm off now.

36:32.360 --> 36:33.640
Goodnight.

36:33.720 --> 36:34.560
Goodnight.

36:44.520 --> 36:46.440
Stop staring.

36:46.520 --> 36:47.560
Naughty ones.

36:54.640 --> 36:56.480
DEAR GRANDMA

36:58.280 --> 36:59.400
Hey, Grandma.

36:59.480 --> 37:01.000
Are you going home yet?

37:01.080 --> 37:02.560
I miss you so much.

37:02.640 --> 37:03.600
Haoan.

37:03.680 --> 37:07.800
Do you have a girlfriend named…

37:08.560 --> 37:10.680
- Her name is Wang Linlin.
- Really?

37:10.760 --> 37:12.680
In a few days, I want to meet her.

37:12.760 --> 37:13.720
Ah?

37:22.200 --> 37:24.800
HAPPY NEW YEAR

37:24.880 --> 37:26.160
Alright.

37:26.240 --> 37:27.200
Okay.

37:28.600 --> 37:31.040
Don't worry. I'll definitely alter
your voice for the media.

37:31.760 --> 37:32.840
Yes.

37:32.920 --> 37:34.840
Your privacy will be completely protected.

37:35.600 --> 37:36.600
Okay, thanks.

37:41.000 --> 37:42.480
Yifan.

37:42.560 --> 37:43.400
Yifan.

37:45.640 --> 37:46.960
Let me show you something fun.

37:48.480 --> 37:49.320
Look.

37:50.080 --> 37:51.120
That interview with your classmate

37:51.200 --> 37:53.360
was featured in the news.

37:53.440 --> 37:54.520
A netizen

37:54.600 --> 37:57.000
compiled a popular news collection.

37:57.080 --> 37:58.160
He included this clip too.

37:58.240 --> 38:00.080
Who knew that it became so popular.

38:00.160 --> 38:01.040
This classmate of yours

38:01.120 --> 38:03.160
made it to the top ten
most popular figures online.

38:03.240 --> 38:04.920
He even trended on social media.

38:06.160 --> 38:07.400
With this clip of him,

38:07.480 --> 38:09.520
our year-end review should be fine.

38:09.600 --> 38:11.280
It really matches what I said,

38:11.360 --> 38:12.400
that he was both amazing and miserable.

38:12.480 --> 38:15.520
Now everyone calls him
"Handsome and Miserable."

38:16.760 --> 38:19.720
You didn't even blur his face out?

38:19.800 --> 38:20.920
Won't it affect him?

38:22.080 --> 38:23.800
No. He signed a consent form.

38:23.880 --> 38:25.040
Look at the comments.

38:25.120 --> 38:26.600
Everyone is praising how handsome he is.

38:27.560 --> 38:29.080
I'll go tell Ms. Liu.

38:29.160 --> 38:30.800
Ms. Liu!

38:42.560 --> 38:44.200
JIANG, HOW ABOUT I MAKE THESE DISHES
FOR YOU DURING THE HOLIDAY?

38:44.280 --> 38:47.080
PREPARING FOR A FAMILY REUNION

38:47.160 --> 38:48.680
SAFE AND HAPPY

39:04.520 --> 39:06.320
Is there anything you want to say now?

39:07.960 --> 39:10.280
Happy… I'm really happy. Happy…

39:10.360 --> 39:12.080
I hope you can be as happy as I am.

39:12.160 --> 39:14.600
Happy…

39:15.200 --> 39:16.480
It's really interesting.

39:17.520 --> 39:19.000
My sister and mom both like watching it.

39:19.600 --> 39:21.880
They even sent this clip
to our big family group.

39:23.080 --> 39:24.400
You scared me to death.

39:26.640 --> 39:27.680
Why are you back?

39:27.760 --> 39:29.760
I rented the apartment myself.

39:29.840 --> 39:31.960
- Wouldn't it be a waste not to stay here?
- True.

39:35.480 --> 39:36.800
But why didn't you
turn on a light at home?

39:46.960 --> 39:49.520
- You're not going back for the holiday?
- It depends on my mood.

39:54.600 --> 39:55.880
Why are there so many things here?

39:56.640 --> 39:58.000
Aren't those two shelves all mine?

40:05.080 --> 40:05.920
Drinking coffee
in the middle of the night?

40:06.000 --> 40:07.520
You might not be able to sleep.

40:12.280 --> 40:13.680
Where's my coffee?

40:15.120 --> 40:16.200
I drank it.

40:16.720 --> 40:18.200
It had already expired,
so I threw it away.

40:18.280 --> 40:19.440
You can drink mine.

40:27.200 --> 40:28.880
How much is it? I'll transfer it to you.

40:29.800 --> 40:30.840
No need.

40:31.720 --> 40:33.840
If I'm not here, help me
deal with the stuff in the fridge.

40:34.880 --> 40:37.080
It can't be stored long anyway.
I don't like wasting things.

40:37.920 --> 40:39.520
Let's just say we bought it together.

40:39.600 --> 40:41.240
How much was it?

40:41.320 --> 40:43.280
Just treat it as me
asking you for a favor.

40:47.360 --> 40:49.160
Didn't we agree

40:49.240 --> 40:50.520
that we'll split all the costs?

41:01.440 --> 41:02.760
A favor?

41:03.800 --> 41:04.960
What kind of favor?

41:11.360 --> 41:13.200
Cleaning up the kitchen scraps?

41:23.240 --> 41:24.760
LET'S CALCULATE IT
HOW MUCH DO I OWE YOU?

41:40.440 --> 41:41.600
Twenty?

41:53.040 --> 41:55.280
YOU OWE ME

41:56.520 --> 41:58.200
When?

42:05.520 --> 42:08.840
Dian, how do you plan
to spend the Spring Festival?

42:08.920 --> 42:10.320
I haven't decided yet.

42:10.400 --> 42:12.160
How about you come
to my place for the holiday?

42:12.240 --> 42:13.080
Let's celebrate together.

42:13.160 --> 42:14.480
Sure.

42:14.560 --> 42:16.440
But I don't feel like running that far.

42:17.360 --> 42:20.200
If you're spending the holiday alone,
won't it be boring?

42:20.280 --> 42:22.440
I plan to sleep for three days and nights.

42:22.520 --> 42:24.160
Make up for all the lost sleep

42:24.240 --> 42:25.920
from all the overtime.

42:26.880 --> 42:27.840
What about Sang Yan?

42:27.920 --> 42:28.920
Is he going home for the holiday?

42:29.000 --> 42:30.400
He'll definitely go home.

42:30.480 --> 42:31.840
His family's local.

42:31.920 --> 42:34.080
And he's not on bad terms with his family.

42:34.600 --> 42:36.560
Why suddenly bring up Sang Yan?

42:36.640 --> 42:38.360
It's just that you never tell me anything

42:38.440 --> 42:39.680
about how you two get along.

42:41.680 --> 42:44.240
We're not really getting along.

42:44.320 --> 42:45.840
Actually, I think

42:46.360 --> 42:48.520
we're more like

42:49.120 --> 42:51.480
two strangers under one roof.

42:53.800 --> 42:56.200
And we don't really talk much.

43:11.480 --> 43:12.320
Six threes.

43:12.400 --> 43:13.560
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

43:13.640 --> 43:14.600
Ten fours.

43:15.280 --> 43:16.360
Ten fives.

43:22.280 --> 43:25.560
Fifteen…

43:25.640 --> 43:26.600
Twenty sixs.

43:28.320 --> 43:29.760
What exactly are you shouting?

43:34.360 --> 43:35.640
I've already self-destructed.

43:35.720 --> 43:36.960
Just yell "open" and you win.

43:38.960 --> 43:40.560
What's that look in your eyes?

43:40.640 --> 43:42.280
Are you calling downward or opening?

43:42.360 --> 43:45.080
Can't you see I've been helping you? Open.

43:46.400 --> 43:47.960
Totally can't tell.

43:48.040 --> 43:49.280
Can't you just say it directly?

43:49.880 --> 43:52.760
Without me, you'd lose every round. Open.

43:53.720 --> 43:55.640
So, does that mean…

43:59.680 --> 44:00.720
Open.

44:01.240 --> 44:02.600
You finally understood what I meant.

44:04.040 --> 44:04.880
I lost.

44:06.240 --> 44:09.720
Sang Yan, you finally lost.
No regrets in my life.

44:09.800 --> 44:12.000
Come on, Truth and Dare.

46:57.120 --> 46:58.040
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

46:58.120 --> 46:58.960
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
